</div><div class="t m5c9 x61 h51 y1ad0 ff1 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Without equal. </div><div class="t m21d x42 h24 y1ad0 ff4 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;At the court of Babylon were gathered rep-</div><div class="t m6e4 x26 h24 y566 ff4 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">resentatives from all lands, men . . . possessed of the broadest </div><div class="t m143 x71 h24 y1b5f ff4 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">culture that the world could bestow; yet among them all, the </div><div class="t m39f x26 h24 y157a ff4 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Hebrew youth were without a peer. In physical strength and </div><div class="t m6a3 x26 h24 y1588 ff4 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">beauty, in mental vigor and literary attainment, they stood un-</div><div class="t m326 x26 h24 y11a8 ff4 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">rivaled. The erect form, the firm, elastic step, the fair counte-</div><div class="t mae7 x26 h24 y156e ff4 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">nance, the undimmed senses, the untainted breath—all </div><div class="t m12b3 xcb h3b y156e ff6 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">were so </div><div class="t mebb x26 h3b y19ce ff6 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">many certificates of good habits, insignia of the nobility with which </div><div class="t md11 x26 h3b y138a ff6 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">nature honors those who are obedient to her laws.&quot;—Prophets and </div><div class="t m1bc5 x26 h3b y405 ff6 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Kings, </div><div class="t m273 x5b h24 y405 ff4 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">p. 485 (italics supplied). </div><div class="t m245 x61 h51 y75d ff1 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">What lesson in changing any health habit does Daniel&apos;s </div><div class="t m322 x26 h51 ya95 ff1 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">experience teach us? </div><div class="t m3f3 x64 h24 y8c2 ff4 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Through His Holy Spirit, God will strengthen us to follow </div><div class="t mae7 x26 h24 y1b70 ff4 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">His plans for our health and happiness. </div><div class="t m1b6 x64 h51 y1544 ff1 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Daniel&apos;s test case was not so much over 